content:
Manage Asset Recalls and Upgrades At Scale

Design timely product service campaigns to effectively assess and address issues on large numbers of products or services. Specify the impacted product, and the priority, duration, status, and type of a campaign. Create work orders and return orders to capture the services to be performed on impacted products.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions with Automotive Cloud. The user interface is available in English only.

Who: Users must have the Product Service Campaign permission set license to use this feature.

How: Create a Product Service Campaign record, specify its details, create Product Service Campaign Item records, relate them to the product service campaign, and create a Return Order or Work Order record from the related list.
title: Automotive Cloud: Product Service Campaigns
